1. *Interesuje* me da li ćeš danas doći. (I'm interested to know if you'll come today.)
2. Kako se *interesuje*š za vožnju biciklom? (How interested are you in biking?)
3. Ona je *interesovala* se za knjigu. (She was interested in the book.)
4. Ona se *interesuje* za politiku. (She is interested in politics.)
5. Mi se *interesujemo* za istoriju. (We are interested in history.)